      <bioghist id="aspace_c5a8c765bbecfe045c70cc395586d403">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Founded in 1925, the American Association for the History of Medicine is the oldest continuously functioning scholarly organization devoted to the study of the history of all aspects of the health profession. Its purpose is to promote interest in the field and encourage research and teaching.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_bc5dc98af1582169ddc9f39a2a2c1c73">
